{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"In a sea surrounded by darkness, two girls were trying to make their escape.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgm":"xinnong-2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Kawakaze!","dir":1,"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"side":2,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Shells from Siren battleships rained down ceaselessly around Kawakaze.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato, please stand back! I shall deal with this!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"What are you saying?! Your equipment is already in tatters!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Falling into the Sirens' trap and endangering Lady Nagato is an unforgivable sin...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Allow me to atone for my transgressions with my life!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The thunderous roar of a cannon was followed by an explosion...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"But when the smoke cleared, it was a mass-produced Sakura battleship that lay in ruins, not Kawakaze.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato, why would you expend your power to protect me...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What are you saying, you fool!","actor":305050,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Lady Nagato?","actor":301490,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":20}],"dir":1,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I am Nagato, Nagato of the Sakura Empire!","actor":305050,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"If I cannot protect even a single comrade, how am I to protect the Sakura Empire?","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady... Nagato...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Having failed to secure the kill, the Siren battleship's movements stopped briefly. Seizing upon that moment...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Witness the power of the Big Seven!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"say":"BOOOM!!!"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The massive guns that bore the weight of protecting a nation rang out. Such power tore apart the enemy with ease.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"In an instant, the enemy forces were engulfed in a sea of fire, and the Siren siege began to fall apart.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato, your power...!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Kawakaze!!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Nagato extended her hand to the injured Kawakaze, half towing her towards their escape route.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"...However, the enemies began to close in on the encumbered Nagato once more.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Lady Nagato, please put me down! You must make it out!","actor":301490,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","dir":1,"side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Ignoring Kawakaze's protests, Nagato raised her formidable rigging, firing back at the encroaching enemies while doing her best to avoid their barrage.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"As Nagato tried to carve out an escape route with her attacks, more Sirens quickly arose to take the place of the fallen.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Lady Nagato!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Kawakaze broke free from Nagato and used the last of her power to charge forward.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The Sakura Empire needs you... Lady Nagato, you must live on...!","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"——","soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/plane","flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"bgm":"story-7"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Suddenly, several bombs rained down upon the approaching Siren forces.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"While your spirit is commendable, you mustn't follow through with that!","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Do you know how sad Nagato would be if she lost you?!","dir":1,"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"side":2,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The night sky glowed brightly with explosions from Zuikaku's dive bombers, which brought an end to their crisis.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Zuikaku... I am in your debt...","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"move","y":-1250,"delay":1.5,"dur":0.25,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"actor":301490},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"In a mix of exhaustion and relief, Kawakaze fell into Zuikaku's bosom.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Kawakaze!","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Don't worry. She's just overwhelmed from having strained herself.","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"You can rest now. That's a good girl.","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"You saved me once again... Thank you, Zuikaku.","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Ah, um, I just happened to be passing by!","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"R-really?","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Yeah, I was just leaving the banquet when these Sirens suddenly showed up, so I thought I'd go teach them a lesson.","actor":307060,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.3,"number":2,"x":20}],"say":"Lady Nagato...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"If the Sirens are here, they must be after Watatsumi...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"There's no reason for you to go out of your way to take such a big risk...","actor":301490,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I disagree. I should be the one to conduct this ritual.","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"More importantly, if the Sirens truly are after Watatsumi, we must never let their plans come to fruition.","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Zuikaku, can I leave Kawakaze with you? She needs to rest.","actor":305050,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Of course! Lady Nagato, Mikasa is waiting for you on the island!","actor":307060,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"dir":1,"side":2}],"mode":2,"continueBgm":true,"fadein":1.5,"id":"FUYINGYINGHUA19"}